	<div id="rpwe_widget-2" class="et_pb_widget rpwe_widget recent-posts-extended"><h4 class="widgettitle">最新消息</h4><div  class="rpwe-block "><ul class="rpwe-ul"><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/5e%e9%bb%8e%e9%9b%a8%e5%b8%8c%e5%90%8c%e5%ad%b8%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%b0%88%e5%93%a1%e5%8d%93%e8%b6%8a%e7%8d%8e%e3%80%8d/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/76bc08e2-6701-4d06-8427-dc305d40cb0f-80x55.jpg" alt="5E黎雨希榮獲「傑出專員卓越獎」"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/5e%e9%bb%8e%e9%9b%a8%e5%b8%8c%e5%90%8c%e5%ad%b8%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%b0%88%e5%93%a1%e5%8d%93%e8%b6%8a%e7%8d%8e%e3%80%8d/" title="Permalink to 5E黎雨希榮獲「傑出專員卓越獎」" rel="bookmark">5E黎雨希榮獲「傑出專員卓越獎」</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">本校一直着重學生在公民教育的培養與發展， &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/5e%e9%bb%8e%e9%9b%a8%e5%b8%8c%e5%90%8c%e5%ad%b8%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%b0%88%e5%93%a1%e5%8d%93%e8%b6%8a%e7%8d%8e%e3%80%8d/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e4%b8%ad%e8%8f%af%e9%a3%b2%e9%a3%9f%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%91%a8%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f%ef%bc%81/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-25-at-10.42.29-AM-80x55.jpeg" alt="中華飲食文化周圓滿結束！"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e4%b8%ad%e8%8f%af%e9%a3%b2%e9%a3%9f%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%91%a8%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f%ef%bc%81/" title="Permalink to 中華飲食文化周圓滿結束！" rel="bookmark">中華飲食文化周圓滿結束！</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">早前，本校舉行了為期五天的「中華飲食文化 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e4%b8%ad%e8%8f%af%e9%a3%b2%e9%a3%9f%e6%96%87%e5%8c%96%e5%91%a8%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e7%b5%90%e6%9d%9f%ef%bc%81/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e6%85%95%e9%9a%aa%e6%a8%82%e5%9c%92%e3%80%8d%e9%80%b2%e9%a7%90%e8%a7%80%e5%a1%98%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-06-at-8.15.43-PM-1-80x55.jpeg" alt="「慕險樂園」進駐觀塘年宵市場"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e6%85%95%e9%9a%aa%e6%a8%82%e5%9c%92%e3%80%8d%e9%80%b2%e9%a7%90%e8%a7%80%e5%a1%98%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4/" title="Permalink to 「慕險樂園」進駐觀塘年宵市場" rel="bookmark">「慕險樂園」進駐觀塘年宵市場</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">農曆新年將至，又是家長帶小朋友外出感受節 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e6%85%95%e9%9a%aa%e6%a8%82%e5%9c%92%e3%80%8d%e9%80%b2%e9%a7%90%e8%a7%80%e5%a1%98%e5%b9%b4%e5%ae%b5%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e5%b8%ab%e7%94%9f%e5%85%89%e5%bd%b1%e3%83%bb%e6%ac%a3%e8%b3%9e%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e3%80%8d%e8%a1%a8%e6%8f%9a%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/622618247_833243653106866_8677657482572537501_n-1-80x55.jpg" alt="「師生光影・欣賞同行」表揚活動"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e5%b8%ab%e7%94%9f%e5%85%89%e5%bd%b1%e3%83%bb%e6%ac%a3%e8%b3%9e%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e3%80%8d%e8%a1%a8%e6%8f%9a%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" title="Permalink to 「師生光影・欣賞同行」表揚活動" rel="bookmark">「師生光影・欣賞同行」表揚活動</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">為肯定同學們在學業與品德上的卓越進步，本 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8c%e5%b8%ab%e7%94%9f%e5%85%89%e5%bd%b1%e3%83%bb%e6%ac%a3%e8%b3%9e%e5%90%8c%e8%a1%8c%e3%80%8d%e8%a1%a8%e6%8f%9a%e6%b4%bb%e5%8b%95/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e9%a6%96%e5%b1%86%e3%80%8c%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b7%a1%e7%a6%ae%e3%80%8d%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e8%88%89%e8%a1%8c/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-03-at-10.36.06-AM-2-80x55.jpeg" alt="首屆「香港生命教育巡禮」圓滿舉行"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e9%a6%96%e5%b1%86%e3%80%8c%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b7%a1%e7%a6%ae%e3%80%8d%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e8%88%89%e8%a1%8c/" title="Permalink to 首屆「香港生命教育巡禮」圓滿舉行" rel="bookmark">首屆「香港生命教育巡禮」圓滿舉行</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">由本校與大自然兩棲及爬蟲教育合辦的「第一 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e9%a6%96%e5%b1%86%e3%80%8c%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%94%9f%e5%91%bd%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b7%a1%e7%a6%ae%e3%80%8d%e5%9c%93%e6%bb%bf%e8%88%89%e8%a1%8c/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e9%87%91%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e7%8d%8e2025%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%89%e9%a0%85%e5%a4%a7%e7%8d%8e/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-03-at-7.39.30-AM-80x55.jpeg" alt="榮獲「金蘋果獎2025」三項大獎"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e9%87%91%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e7%8d%8e2025%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%89%e9%a0%85%e5%a4%a7%e7%8d%8e/" title="Permalink to 榮獲「金蘋果獎2025」三項大獎" rel="bookmark">榮獲「金蘋果獎2025」三項大獎</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">早前，本校創新科技教育組前赴澳門科學館， &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e9%87%91%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e7%8d%8e2025%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%89%e9%a0%85%e5%a4%a7%e7%8d%8e/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%9c%ac%e6%a0%a1%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e9%81%8a%e5%ad%b8%e5%9c%98%e3%80%8d%e5%98%89%e8%a8%b1%e7%a6%ae%e6%ae%8a%e6%a6%ae/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/WhatsApp-Image-2026-02-02-at-9.28.55-AM-80x55.jpeg" alt="榮獲「傑出學校遊學團」嘉許禮殊榮"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%9c%ac%e6%a0%a1%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e9%81%8a%e5%ad%b8%e5%9c%98%e3%80%8d%e5%98%89%e8%a8%b1%e7%a6%ae%e6%ae%8a%e6%a6%ae/" title="Permalink to 榮獲「傑出學校遊學團」嘉許禮殊榮" rel="bookmark">榮獲「傑出學校遊學團」嘉許禮殊榮</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">慕光英文書院校榮獲第二屆「傑出學校遊學團 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e6%9c%ac%e6%a0%a1%e6%a6%ae%e7%8d%b2%e3%80%8c%e5%82%91%e5%87%ba%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e9%81%8a%e5%ad%b8%e5%9c%98%e3%80%8d%e5%98%89%e8%a8%b1%e7%a6%ae%e6%ae%8a%e6%a6%ae/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li><li class="rpwe-li rpwe-clearfix"><a class="rpwe-img" href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8cai-x-steam01-%e6%8c%91%e6%88%b0%e8%b3%bd%e3%80%8d%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e/"  rel="bookmark"><img class="rpwe-alignright rpwe-thumb" src="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WhatsApp-Image-2026-01-26-at-7.30.08-PM-2-80x55.jpeg" alt="獲頒AI x STEAM+01挑戰賽 獎項"></a><h3 class="rpwe-title"><a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8cai-x-steam01-%e6%8c%91%e6%88%b0%e8%b3%bd%e3%80%8d%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e/" title="Permalink to 獲頒AI x STEAM+01挑戰賽 獎項" rel="bookmark">獲頒AI x STEAM+01挑戰賽 獎項</a></h3><div class="rpwe-summary">本校一直致力於推動創新教育，鼓勵教師將尖 &hellip;<a href="https://www.mukuang.edu.hk/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b6%88%e6%81%af/%e3%80%8cai-x-steam01-%e6%8c%91%e6%88%b0%e8%b3%bd%e3%80%8d%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e/" class="more-link">Read More »</a></div></li></ul></div><!-- Generated by http://wordpress.org/plugins/recent-posts-widget-extended/ --></div><div id="execphp-2" class="et_pb_widget widget_execphp">			<div class="execphpwidget"><iframe src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=mukuang.edu.hk_ssia00l82gfbsfo5f1dt8tgktk%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Asia%2FHong_Kong" style="border: 0" width="400" height="400" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div>
